{"tid":2296434,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我為了炒股去了商務買了老子同莊子","createTime":"2020-11-22T13:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T05:44:22.000Z","uid":330728,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a30db637912bf18c6b74d98a929a5e0f30b83f8f","tid":2296434,"uid":330728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:03:26.000Z","msg":"股票讓我學會的道理 ：<br />\n弱水三千，只取一瓢"},{"pid":"565faebd3e6df13bc1934dc02e5e9cf4165ac0bb","tid":2296434,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T04:47:59.000Z","msg":"五色令人目盲；五音令人耳聾；五味令人口爽；馳騁田獵，令人心發狂；難得之貨，令人行妨。"},{"pid":"744a0f56d63895e103dc77d174bc9274eab793a7","tid":2296434,"uid":366156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T04:54:39.000Z","msg":"藍店商務"},{"pid":"79222545f3ea0fcccb39989d229a59bd42912997","tid":2296434,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"天下莫柔弱於水，而攻堅強者莫之能勝，其無以易之。弱之勝強，柔之勝剛，天下莫不知，莫能行。"},{"pid":"e46b232cf221310998f8a32564b162b44bace1e1","tid":2296434,"uid":308853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"寵辱若驚，貴大患若身。何謂寵辱若驚？寵為下，得之若驚，失之若驚，是謂寵辱若驚。何謂貴大患若身？吾所以有大患者，為吾有身，及吾無身，吾有何患？"},{"pid":"e58d7f6a1914ac0cd0ef31cf17be72cc368318d4","tid":2296434,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:01:04.000Z","msg":"大成若缺，其用不弊。大盈若沖，其用不窮。大直若屈，大巧若拙，大辯若訥。"},{"pid":"61335546e48ed73784f82a3fc5cb1df174e05d80","tid":2296434,"uid":326779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:44:22.000Z","msg":"吾生也有涯，而知也無涯，以有涯隨無涯，殆也"}]}